communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Washington Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

The current index of records maintained by Washington Technology Solutions pursuant to RCW 42.56.070(5).

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes. I would prefer the request filled electronically if possible.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Kevin Wallace
